		<outline text="3/18/2017" created="Sat, 18 Mar 2017 17:01:34 GMT" >
			<outline text="Why is the menu in the title bar crazy?" created="Sat, 18 Mar 2017 17:01:34 GMT" type="outline" >
				<outline text="Next question --&amp;nbsp;" created="Sat, 18 Mar 2017 17:01:35 GMT" />
				<outline text="Why is the menubar for my &lt;a href=&quot;http://pork.io/electric/linux/Electric-Pork-linux-x64.zip&quot;&gt;app&lt;/a&gt; so crazy?" created="Sat, 18 Mar 2017 17:01:36 GMT" />
